title: Skinny Funfetti Dip
directions: Pour yogurt and Cool Whip into the bowl of your stand mixer. Start blending.
Slowly add the entire box of dry funfetti cake mix.
Whip until completely smooth. I had to put mine on high for a few minutes to fully get it blended and with no lumps. If you taste yogurt in it, it’s not mixed well enough.
Put it in the fridge for 3 hours (or overnight).
Serve with fruit, animal crackers, or whatever your favorite thing to “dunk” is.
-Total: 2920 divided by 24 servings for a mere 120 calories for 1/2 cup serving!
Adapted from: Kelly at Eat Yourself Skinny.
ingredients: 1 package Light Cool Whip (8 Ounce Package)
1 package Funfetti Cake Mix, 18 Ounce Box
